# === Google Sign-In (Production Only - No localhost) ===
#
# Important: These are configured in Supabase Dashboard, not here.
# Client ID & Secret are safely stored in Supabase → Authentication → Providers → Google
#
# In Supabase → Authentication → URL Configuration, make sure these Redirect URLs are added:
#   https://app.t360.in/weblogin/
#   https://app.t360.in/weblogin
#   https://api.t360.in/auth/v1/callback   (already there)
#
# In your code (signInWithGoogle function), use:
# redirectTo: `${window.location.origin}/weblogin/`   (on web)
